             was indicted for <rs id="t18020428-111-off587" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18020428-111-off587" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18020428-111-off587" type="offenceSubcategory" value="housebreaking"></interp>
               breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18020428-111-victim823" type="victimName">
                           Benjamin 
                           Ames
                        <interp inst="t18020428-111-victim823" type="surname" value="Ames"></interp>
